1
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:24,159
If you can survive to the end,

2
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:26,159
the reward isn't just money and medicine.

3
00:01:26,239 --> 00:01:26,799
Moreover,

4
00:01:26,799 --> 00:01:28,400
you can choose one of them

5
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,480
to bring back to reality.

6
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,439
What?

7
00:01:32,599 --> 00:01:34,480
Bring back to the real world?

8
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:36,000
Are you serious?

9
00:01:36,439 --> 00:01:37,439
Think carefully.

10
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:39,400
Who do you want to bring back the most?

11
00:01:47,599 --> 00:01:49,000
I never thought

12
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,159
there would be a future with them.

13
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:08,199
This is so messed up.

14
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:10,400
Shouldn't I be focusing on

15
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,159
fighting Gu Zhantian with all my might right now?

16
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,759
Lu Chengwen,

17
00:02:20,199 --> 00:02:21,759
prepare all your assets.

18
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,000
Otherwise,

19
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,159
the lives of these four

20
00:02:24,199 --> 00:02:25,560
won't be guaranteed.

21
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,000
I didn't expect

22
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,280
Gu Zhantian to be so ruthless.

23
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:33,840
Gu Zhantian,

24
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,479
here is the asset transfer contract.

25
00:03:36,879 --> 00:03:38,280
Let all four of them go.

26
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,800
Put away that

27
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,080
hypocritical look of yours.

28
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,680
Gu Zhantian,

29
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:48,639
don't do anything stupid.

30
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,479
You are the Righteous Male Lead.

31
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,240
Righteous Male Lead?

32
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,000
Righteous Male Lead?

33
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:57,319
Does the Righteous Male Lead deserve to be used,

34
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,240
bullied, and humiliated by you?

35
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,000
Then I'd rather be a villain.

36
00:04:01,479 --> 00:04:02,719
You don't have to do this.

37
00:04:03,199 --> 00:04:04,919
I brought the asset transfer contract.

38
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,680
I'm giving you all my assets.

39
00:04:06,919 --> 00:04:08,400
Do whatever you want.

40
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,800
Devour the four major families,

41
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,840
devour Haicheng.

42
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,280
Just let them go,

43
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,919
and go back to being your Righteous Male Lead.

44
00:04:13,919 --> 00:04:14,479
Okay?

45
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:16,560
I, Gu Zhantian,

46
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:18,399
have roamed the world for so many years.

47
00:04:19,199 --> 00:04:21,680
I've always been the one telling others to be good.

48
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,279
Who do you think you are

49
00:04:23,879 --> 00:04:25,399
to pretend to be righteous in front of me?

50
00:04:26,519 --> 00:04:27,319
Fine.

51
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,639
I've changed my mind now.

52
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,439
These four,

53
00:04:31,439 --> 00:04:33,120
aren't they devoted to you?

54
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:35,279
All your assets

55
00:04:35,279 --> 00:04:36,680
can only be exchanged for one.

56
00:04:37,439 --> 00:04:39,120
As for the other three, let me think.

57
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:41,120
Should I let them be buried with you,

58
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:43,920
or take them to the border as slaves?

59
00:04:45,319 --> 00:04:46,120
Choose!

60
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,639
I told you to choose!

61
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,279
I choose...

62
00:05:15,879 --> 00:05:16,680
Jiang Shihan.

63
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,839
Jiang Shihan, huh?

64
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,399
Mr. Lu.

65
00:05:37,399 --> 00:05:38,639
How ridiculous.

66
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,279
Look at the three of you.

67
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,040
You gave up all your assets,

68
00:05:44,639 --> 00:05:45,639
but in the end,

69
00:05:46,439 --> 00:05:48,839
he doesn't care if you live or die.

70
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:50,879
Isn't that right,

71
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,720
Qingqiu?

72
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,199
Answer me.

73
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,600
Lu Chengwen,

74
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:03,079
you really are a piece of trash.

75
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:07,839
What's wrong?

76
00:06:09,279 --> 00:06:10,279
You want to say something?

77
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:11,839
What is it?

78
00:06:14,639 --> 00:06:15,399
Lu Chengwen,

79
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:17,120
we are cutting ties from now on.

80
00:06:17,399 --> 00:06:18,319
Never contact me again.

81
00:06:18,879 --> 00:06:20,120
That's more like it.

82
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,680
Brother Zhantian,

83
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:29,120
I was tricked by that jerk before.

84
00:06:29,439 --> 00:06:30,720
After what happened this time,

85
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,000
I've thought it through.

86
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:34,000
I will only be with you from now on.

87
00:06:38,279 --> 00:06:39,399
Brother Zhantian,

88
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:41,319
you tied me so tight it hurts.

89
00:06:41,439 --> 00:06:43,279
Who told you to be so disobedient before?

90
00:06:48,399 --> 00:06:49,199
Zhantian,

91
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:51,519
as long as you help me get rid of Lu Chengwen,

92
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,800
all of my and the Leng family's assets

93
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,720
will be yours.

94
00:06:55,399 --> 00:06:56,199
Mr. Gu,

95
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:57,720
the Chen family is also willing to ally with you.

96
00:06:58,439 --> 00:06:59,560
As long as you help me teach this

97
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,839
ungrateful man a lesson.

98
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:02,120
Lu Chengwen,

99
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:04,639
it seems it's heaven's will for me to kill you.

100
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,639
Then don't blame me.

101
00:07:07,079 --> 00:07:08,399
It seems

102
00:07:08,399 --> 00:07:10,040
a battle between us is inevitable.

103
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,279
How about this?

104
00:07:11,439 --> 00:07:12,240
Let's keep it simple.

105
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:13,920
One move to decide the winner.

106
00:07:14,839 --> 00:07:15,439
So that

107
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:17,000
we don't get blood everywhere

108
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,319
and scare them.

109
00:07:21,399 --> 00:07:22,240
Brother Zhantian,

110
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,120
I'm scared.

111
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:25,240
Zhantian,

112
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:26,519
let's make this quick.

113
00:07:26,879 --> 00:07:28,240
I don't want to see him again.

114
00:07:28,839 --> 00:07:29,639
Zhantian,

115
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,800
finish this early so we can go see Grandpa.

116
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,600
Don't waste your energy on him.

117
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:38,399
Alright.

118
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,600
One move it is.

119
00:07:42,639 --> 00:07:43,680
Take this!

120
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,000
Immovable Wisdom King!

121
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,639
Unseal!

122
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:52,839
Immovable Underworld King!

123
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,040
Chengwen!

124
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:01,839
Chengwen!

125
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:21,839
You can hear me,

126
00:08:21,839 --> 00:08:22,639
right?

127
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:26,199
Good.

128
00:08:26,199 --> 00:08:26,879
Then next,

129
00:08:26,879 --> 00:08:27,720
we'll do this.

130
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:29,720
Brother Zhantian,

131
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,600
I'm scared.

132
00:08:54,279 --> 00:08:54,879
Chengwen!

133
00:08:54,879 --> 00:08:55,679
Chengwen!

134
00:08:55,919 --> 00:08:56,720
How are you?

135
00:08:59,919 --> 00:09:00,720
I'm fine.

136
00:09:06,919 --> 00:09:07,720
Heavenly Dao,

137
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,240
Gu Zhantian has already lost.

138
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,519
Aren't you going to show yourself?

139
00:09:30,639 --> 00:09:31,759
You

140
00:09:31,759 --> 00:09:33,519
are not my people.

141
00:09:33,919 --> 00:09:34,919
Why

142
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:36,679
are you in my world?

143
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:39,399
To help them break the plot loop.

144
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,240
To

145
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:43,000
help them break their destined fate.

146
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:45,000
And more importantly,

147
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,000
to go back and save my mom.

148
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,000
It's your turn,

149
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,519
Liu Ye.

150
00:10:10,799 --> 00:10:12,679
I am the Heavenly Dao of this world.

151
00:10:12,879 --> 00:10:13,879
Did you think

152
00:10:13,879 --> 00:10:15,440
you could kill me?

153
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,519
Don't speak too soon.

154
00:10:18,039 --> 00:10:18,840
Release!

155
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:24,440
Gu Zhantian!

156
00:10:24,639 --> 00:10:25,720
Stop playing dead!

157
00:10:26,279 --> 00:10:27,080
Get him!

158
00:10:31,799 --> 00:10:32,919
Gu Zhantian!

159
00:10:35,399 --> 00:10:36,039
Lu Chengwen!

160
00:10:36,039 --> 00:10:37,440
What is sealed inside your body now

161
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,200
is the true qi I drained from my whole body

162
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:41,279
to form the Immovable Underworld King Art for you.

163
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,399
Remember,

164
00:10:42,639 --> 00:10:44,320
you only have one chance to use it.

165
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,279
Don't worry.

166
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,519
I will definitely

167
00:10:54,519 --> 00:10:55,840
use it at the most critical moment.

168
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:57,120
If you want to kill me in one strike,

169
00:10:57,519 --> 00:10:58,840
you must seal my Ghost Acupoint.

170
00:11:01,639 --> 00:11:02,200
Here

171
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,360
is my weak spot.
